      "plain": "Sail to the Sun Logbook: Your cruising editor once lived aboard here while working for Waterway Guide when they were based out of Annapolis, and loved it. It is convenient to some of Annapolis\u2019s best pubs and restaurants, gives easy access to and from the Bay, and it is only a short walk over the bridge to downtown Annapolis \u2014 and an easy stagger back. Transient dockage is available, but book ahead, especially during the fall Sailboat Show."
