    "local_notes": {
      "annapolis_context": "Sail to the Sun Logbook: Annapolis is America\u2019s sailing capital, and you will know it the moment you cruise into town. If there is something you need, you will probably find it here, from Bacon\u2019s, https://baconsails.com/, the quintessential consignment shop, to boutique marine stores and competent yacht yards. If you are looking for crabcakes, Davis\u2019 Pub is your best stop. Good burgers too. During the show, do not be surprised to see major sailing names there. It is Annapolis. If you as a sailor do not feel right at home in Annapolis, you will never feel at home anywhere."
